=begin pod

... and we will join all the code sections together...
=end pod

    } # end of my Str $raku-code = @submatches.map(
    ).join;

=begin pod 1
=head3 remove blank lines at the end

=end pod

    $raku-code ~~ s{\n  <blank-line>* $ } = '';

=begin pod

And that's the end of the C<tangle> subroutine!
=end pod
